# Prossfora Frontend - Complete Development Plan

## ðŸ“‹ Project Overview
Complete the Prossfora contractor management platform frontend with full functionality, user authentication, real-time features, and production-ready deployment.

---

## Phase 1: Core Infrastructure & Authentication (Week 1-2)

### 1.1 Authentication System
- [ ] **JWT Token Management**
  - Implement token storage strategy (in-memory/cookies)
  - Create axios interceptor for automatic token refresh
  - Build protected route wrapper component
  - Handle token expiration and auto-logout

- [ ] **Auth Pages - Full Implementation**
  - [ ] Sign In page with form validation
  - [ ] Sign Up page with role selection (Customer/Contractor)
  - [ ] Forgot Password flow
  - [ ] Reset Password page
  - [ ] Email verification page
  - [ ] Error handling and user feedback

- [ ] **Auth Context Provider**
  - Global auth state management
  - User session persistence
  - Role-based access control (RBAC)
  - Auto-redirect based on user role

### 1.2 API Integration Layer
- [ ] **API Client Setup**
  - Create centralized axios instance with base URL
  - Environment variable configuration (.env)
  - Request/response interceptors
  - Error handling middleware
  - Loading state management

- [ ] **API Service Functions**
  - User service (CRUD operations)
  - Job service (create, update, list, filter)
  - Financial service (transactions, payouts)
  - Analytics service (stats, reports)
  - Upload service (file/image handling)

### 1.3 State Management
- [ ] **Choose & Implement State Solution**
  - Option A: React Context + useReducer
  - Option B: Zustand (lightweight)
  - Option C: Redux Toolkit (complex apps)
  
- [ ] **Global State Stores**
  - User/Auth state
  - Notifications/Alerts
  - UI state (sidebar, modals)
  - Cache management

